      "content": "rebuilding feels like such a joke though. why would i want to spend the rest of my life trying to fix something that's fundamentally broken? honestly, the version of me that was successful/good/valued is gone. it's much more peaceful to just accept that it's finished. wouldn't it be easier to just let it go completely?",
